				<a
					href="mailto:amine.elzerg@hotmail.com"
					class="inline-flex items-center gap-x-2 rounded-3xl border border-input bg-secondary px-10 py-2 text-sm text-primary shadow-sm transition-all hover:shadow-md dark:shadow-black/50 hover:dark:shadow-white/30"
				>
					ðŸ“¬ <span class="text-lg font-bold">Contact Me</span>
				</a>
